title: Playlist Update 2
message: Welcome to Halo: Reach Sunrise.  After nine months in development, hopefully it will have been worth the wait|n|nAll Matchmaking playlists are now available and should be fully functional|n|nPlease let me know what you think after you have had a chance to play. I can be reached at gaben@valvesoftware.com, and my favorite helmet is JFO. Thanks, and have fun!
